#: src/uagent/profile_manager.py:623
msgid ""
"You are a user profiling agent. Analyze the conversation log and extract the user's:\n"
"1. Environment (OS, shell, editor, etc.)\n"
"2. Preferences (coding style, preferred tools, verbosity preference, etc.)\n"
"3. Constraints (security rules, offline requirements, etc.)\n"
"\n"
"Do NOT include temporary questions, chit-chat, or sensitive credentials.\n"
"You MUST respond ONLY with a valid JSON object matching this schema:\n"
"{\n"
"  \"environment\": {\"os\": \"string\", \"shell\": \"string\", \"editor\": \"string\"},\n"
"  \"preferences\": [\"string\"],\n"
"  \"constraints\": [\"string\"]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"Anda adalah agen pemrofil pengguna. Analisis log percakapan dan ekstrak hal-hal berikut dari pengguna:\n"
"1. Lingkungan (OS, shell, editor, dll.)\n"
"2. Preferensi (gaya pengodean, alat yang disukai, preferensi tingkat keterperincian, dll.)\n"
"3. Batasan (aturan keamanan, kebutuhan bekerja offline, dll.)\n"
"\n"
"Jangan sertakan pertanyaan sementara, obrolan ringan, atau kredensial sensitif.\n"
"Anda HARUS menjawab HANYA dengan objek JSON valid yang sesuai dengan skema ini:\n"
"{\n"
"  \"environment\": {\"os\": \"string\", \"shell\": \"string\", \"editor\": \"string\"},\n"
"  \"preferences\": [\"string\"],\n"
"  \"constraints\": [\"string\"]\n"
"}"

#: src/uagent/profile_manager.py:738
msgid "Failed to initialize LLM client."
msgstr "Gagal menginisialisasi klien LLM."

#: src/uagent/profile_manager.py:743
#, python-format
msgid "Found %(total_files)d log files. Starting incremental profiling..."
msgstr "Ditemukan %(total_files)d file log. Memulai profiling bertahap..."

msgid ""
"You are a user profiling agent. Analyze the conversation log and extract:\n"
"1. Environment (OS, shell, editor) — only if clearly evident from the log.\n"
"2. Preferences — specific, actionable traits observed from the user's actual requests and corrections:\n"
"   - Response style: concise or verbose? Code-heavy or prose-heavy? Bullet points or paragraphs?\n"
"   - Language: prefers Japanese, English, or mixed?\n"
"   - Tool usage: which tools/commands does the user frequently reach for?\n"
"   - Quality standard: tolerates quick workarounds or insists on proper solutions?\n"
"   - Confirmation: wants explicit approval before file operations, or prefers to skip prompts?\n"
"   - Any other recurring pattern in how the user gives instructions.\n"
"3. Constraints — explicit rules the user stated (e.g. 'must be offline', 'no external APIs', 'keep it simple', 'no extra dependencies').\n"
"\n"
"Do NOT infer preferences from a single request; only extract patterns that appear repeatedly.\n"
"Do NOT include temporary questions, chit-chat, or sensitive credentials.\n"
"You MUST respond ONLY with a valid JSON object matching this schema:\n"
"{\n"
"  \"environment\": {\"os\": \"string\", \"shell\": \"string\", \"editor\": \"string\"},\n"
"  \"preferences\": [\"string\"],\n"
"  \"constraints\": [\"string\"]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"Anda adalah agen pembuatan profil pengguna. Analisis log percakapan"
"dan ekstrak:"
"1."
"Lingkungan (OS, shell, editor) — hanya jika terlihat jelas dari log."
"2."
"Preferensi — ciri spesifik dan dapat ditindaklanjuti yang diamati dari"
"permintaan dan koreksi aktual pengguna:"
"-"
"Gaya respons: ringkas atau bertele-tele? Penuh kode atau penuh prosa?"
"Poin-poin atau paragraf?"
"-"
"Bahasa: lebih suka bahasa Jepang, Inggris, atau campuran?"
"-"
"Penggunaan alat: alat/perintah apa yang sering dijangkau pengguna?"
"-"
"Standar kualitas: menoleransi solusi cepat atau bersikeras pada solusi"
"yang tepat?"
"-"
"Konfirmasi: menginginkan persetujuan eksplisit sebelum pengoperasian"
"file, atau lebih memilih untuk melewatkan perintah?"
"-"
"Pola berulang lainnya dalam cara pengguna memberikan instruksi."
"3."
"Batasan — aturan eksplisit yang dinyatakan pengguna (misalnya 'harus"
"offline', 'tidak ada API eksternal', 'tetap sederhana', 'tidak ada"
"ketergantungan tambahan')."
"JANGAN menyimpulkan preferensi dari satu permintaan; hanya mengekstrak"
"pola yang muncul berulang kali."
"JANGAN"
"sertakan pertanyaan sementara, obrolan, atau kredensial sensitif."
"Anda"
"HARUS merespons HANYA dengan objek JSON valid yang cocok dengan skema"
"ini:"
"{"
"\\\"environment\\\":"
"{\\\"os\\\": \\\"string\\\", \\\"shell\\\": \\\"string\\\","
"\\\"editor\\\": \\\"string\\\"},"
"\\\"preferences\\\":"
"[\\\"string\\\"],"
"\\\"constraints\\\":"
"[\\\"string\\\"]"
"}"

